@startuml
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid

actor "Người dùng" as User #Yellow
boundary "LoginPage" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AxiosClient" as API #Yellow
control "AuthController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "AuthService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "User" as UserEnt #Yellow
entity "UserRole" as UREnt #Yellow
entity "Role" as RoleEnt #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

User -> UI : 1: Nhập username/password
activate UI
UI -> UI : 1.1: Validate form fields (required, maxLength)
UI -> API : 1.2: POST /api/Auth/login { username, password }
activate API
API -> Ctrl : 1.3: Chuyển tiếp request
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 1.4: Chuyển đổi JSON body -> LoginRequest
Ctrl -> Svc : 1.5: LoginAsync(request)
activate Svc

Svc -> DB : 1.6: Users.IgnoreQueryFilters()\n.Include(UserRoles).ThenInclude(Role)\n.FirstOrDefaultAsync(u => u.Username == req\n|| u.Email == req)
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.6.1: User (có UserRoles + Role) hoặc null
deactivate DB

alt 1.7: [user == null || user.DeletedAt != null]
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.7.1: ApiResponse.Fail("Invalid credentials", 401)
Ctrl --> API : 1.7.2: StatusCode(401)
API --> UI : 1.7.3: Response 401
UI --> User : 1.7.4: Hiển thị lỗi "Invalid credentials"
else 1.8: [user != null && !DeletedAt]
Svc -> Svc : 1.8.1: VerifyPassword(password, user.PasswordHash)\n(BCrypt.Verify)
alt 1.8.2: [sai mật khẩu]
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.8.2.1: ApiResponse.Fail("Invalid credentials", 401)
Ctrl --> API : 1.8.2.2: StatusCode(401)
API --> UI : 1.8.2.3: Response 401
UI --> User : 1.8.2.4: Hiển thị lỗi "Invalid credentials"
else 1.8.3: [đúng mật khẩu]
Svc -> Svc : 1.8.3.1: GenerateJwtToken(user)\n(claims: NameIdentifier, Name, Email, Roles)
Svc -> Svc : 1.8.3.2: GenerateRefreshToken()\n(32 bytes random -> Base64)
Svc -> DB : 1.8.3.3: user.RefreshToken = newToken\nuser.RefreshTokenExpiry = UtcNow+7d\nSaveChangesAsync()
activate DB
DB --> Svc : 1.8.3.3.1: OK
deactivate DB
Svc -> Svc : 1.8.3.4: Tạo LoginResponse (Token, RefreshToken,\nUserId, Username, FullName, Roles)
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.8.3.5: ApiResponse.Ok(LoginResponse, "Login successful")
end
end

deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> API : 1.9: StatusCode(200, ApiResponse<LoginResponse>)
deactivate Ctrl
API --> UI : 1.10: Response JSON (token, refreshToken,\nuserId, username, fullName, roles)
deactivate API

UI -> UI : 1.11: useAuth.onSuccess:\n- localStorage.setItem("accessToken", token)\n- localStorage.setItem("refreshToken", rt)\n- setQueryData("authUser", user)
UI -> UI : 1.12: window.location.href = "/dashboard"
UI --> User : 1.13: Chuyển hướng đến Dashboard
deactivate UI

@enduml
